(8762, 'itIT', 'Metzen la Renna', 'Rescue Metzen the Reindeer from his captors near Growless Cave in Hillsbrad Foothills.', 'Che disastro! Metzen la Renna è stato rapito!$B$BMetzen è una delle otto renne di Babbo Inverno... ed è di proprietà della Masseria Buongusto. Abbiamo ricevuto non una, ma ben DUE lettere di riscatto da gruppi che sostengono di avere Metzen. Ed essendo nel pieno della stagione delle feste, abbiamo risorse limitate! Ti prego, trova Metzen e riportacelo!$B$BEsamina le lettere di riscatto alla ricerca d\'indizi. Quando troverai Metzen, cospargilo con questa polvere di renna: lo libererà da qualsiasi catena!$B$BTi prego, sbrigati!', '', '', '', '', '', '', 29981),
(8500, 'itIT', 'L\'Alleanza ha bisogno di altri Lingotti di Torio!', 'Porta 20 Lingotti di Torio a Dama Trecciadoppia nell\'Aerodromo di Dun Morogh.', '$n, che piacere rivederti. Spero tu stia bene. Sì, è vero, abbiamo bisogno di altri Lingotti di Torio. Se ne avessi con te, io li sto ancora raccogliendo per i preparativi per la guerra di Ahn\'qiraj.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 29981),
(8419, 'itIT', 'An Imp\'s Request', 'Bring a piece of felcloth to Impsy in Felwood.', '$n, an imp in Felwood by the name of Impsy has requested your presence.  It is somewhat strange, as he has asked that you bring a piece of felcloth as a sign of good faith.  Considering the power you already wield as a warlock, I can only assume you know the satyrs of Felwood carry this felcloth.$b$bYou can find Impsy just north of the Bloodvenom Falls, which I\'ve heard is quite lovely this time of year.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 29981),
(8288, 'itIT', 'Only One May Rise', 'Return the Head of the Broodlord Lashlayer to Baristolth of the Shifting Sands at Cenarion Hold in Silithus.', 'There is no time to waste! A hero must be found! The task I give will require an army to complete but only one may rise from the throng of would be champions to take on the burden and responsibility of an ally of the Brood.$B$BWithin the lair of the Lord of Blackrock is a most cruel beast. The Broodlord Lashlayer guards the Halls of Strife, blocking the way into Nefarian\'s inner sanctum. Slay the foul aberration and return his head to me. Do this and you may begin the next step of your journey.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 29981),
(8275, 'itIT', 'Taking Back Silithus', 'Talk to Windcaller Proudhorn at Cenarion Hold in Silithus.', 'Attention, heroes of the Alliance!  The silithid menace has been left unchecked for too long.  Unfettered by any real opposition, they\'ve been preparing all this time for a large-scale expansion.  $B$BCenarion Circle forces are gathering in Silithus to take the fight to these wretched creatures and all able-bodied adventurers are hereby called to join us!$B$BDon\'t wait until it\'s too late!  Aid us in the defense of Azeroth! Report to Windcaller Proudhorn at Cenarion Hold for specific instructions!', '', '', '', '', '', '', 29981),
