UPDATE `quest_template_locale` SET `LogTitle`='Heart of Rage', `QuestDescription`='$C, you must gather a group to investigate the Blood Furnace inside Hellfire Citadel at once!$B$BThe magical scrying that we have at our disposal indicates that something unnatural is occurring in there.  But a powerful force inside is blocking any detailed arcane investigations, so it must be very important.$B$BYou should expect heavy resistance - no other mission that we\'ve sent in there has ever returned!$B$BScout it entirely and then report back to Nazgrel, advisor to Thrall, with what you witness.', `AreaDescription`='Fully Investigate The Blood Furnace', `VerifiedBuild`=29981 WHERE (`ID`=9608 AND `locale`='itIT');
UPDATE `quest_template_locale` SET `LogTitle`='Weaken the Ramparts', `QuestDescription`='Quick, there isn\'t much time.  Thrallmar\'s existence balances on the razor\'s edge!$B$BWe\'re caught between Hellfire Citadel in the west and the Burning Legion to the east.  With the Legion\'s attention turned toward the Dark Portal we must take this opportunity to strike at the fel orcs of Hellfire Citadel.  The key to this is to first break through their ramparts!$B$BGo there, slay their leaders, and then bring back proof to Caza\'rez across the room from me!', `VerifiedBuild`=29981 WHERE (`ID`=9572 AND `locale`='itIT');
